"""Stage A — locked-prior warm-start.

Consumes:
  - `surface_registration_v2.get_surface_registration(s)` — 2-D PWR fit, gives
    (t_x, t_y) and a residual θ correction.
  - `roi_area_sxy.estimate_sxy_roi_area(sid)` — per-cell tight xy-bbox sxy.
    Falls back to the PWR-stage1 affine-derived sxy on 782149 (where roi
    has known −15 % bias) and on intensity subjects (no metrics.pickle).
  - `surfaces_iter08.get_cz_surface_iter08`, `get_hcr_top_surface_iter07` —
    image-only pia surfaces; used for the tilt-residual rotation R_tilt and
    the t_z anchor (CZ pia mapped onto HCR pia at the CZ centroid xy).

Pins 5 of the 7 affine DOF before any 3-D centroid matching:
  R = R_180 @ R_tilt
  (s_x, s_y) = (sxy, sxy)            (sz left at 1.0 — Stage B's job)
  (t_x, t_y) from PWR rigid+affine
  t_z so that the (rotated, scaled) CZ pia z at the cloud-mean xy equals
       HCR pia z at the same point.

API
---
* :class:`LockedPriorWarmStart` — dataclass with everything pinned.
* :func:`compute_locked_prior_warm_start(s)` — run from scratch.
* :func:`apply_to_cz_um(lp, cz_zyx_um)` — produce warped CZ centroids in HCR µm.
"""
